Class CommandFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • hjz_zork.CommandFactory

  • class CommandFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory class which generates Command objects for the Zork interpreter.

    1.0, 11/15/2016
    Author:
    Hollis Pultz, John Pruchnic, Zachary Zwierko
